snippet.title: WRC 9 | New Zealand Gameplay
snippet.description:
In the brand-new New Zealand Rally, players will face a tough challenge along the rugged coastline and wild lands around Auckland in the heart of the North Island. 

#WRC9 will release on September 3 on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, Epic Games Store, and at a later date on Xbox Series X and PlayStation and Nintendo Switch. 

-------------------------------
